## Release Notes

This will appear in the release notes 😃

## Change Type

Indicate the type of change your pull request is:

- [ ] `patch` - 🐛 Bug Fix
- [ ] `minor` - 🚀 Enhancement
- [ ] `major` - 💥 Breaking Change
- [ ] `internal` - 🏠 Internal
- [ ] `documentation` - 📝 Documentation
- [ ] `tests` - 🧪 Tests
- [ ] `dependencies` - 🔩 Dependency Updates
- [ ] `performance` - 🏎 Performance
- [ ] `skip-release`
